---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Me – Cristóbal Maturana"
  description="Learn about Cristóbal Maturana, documentary photographer and visual storyteller."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-layout">
        <div class="about-photo">
          <img
            src="https://crismaturana.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1505-2-3-684x1024.jpg"
            alt="Cristóbal Maturana"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="about-body">
          <p class="section-label">Photographer & Visual Storyteller</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Hi there, I'm Cristóbal Maturana.</h2>
          <p>
            Photographer, visual storyteller, and passionate about capturing what makes you truly different.
          </p>
          <p>
            For me, photography is not just technique — it's connection. It's about seeing beyond the surface and revealing the essence of a person, a brand, a moment. I specialize in creating authentic images with depth, character, and soul — photographs that genuinely reflect who you are.
          </p>
          <p>
            I approach every session with intention and sensitivity. I pay close attention to light, composition, and the subtle gestures that often speak the loudest. Because a powerful image isn't just beautiful — it feels real.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether it's portraiture, artistic photography, or a personal project, I take the time to understand your story and translate it into images that speak without words.
          </p>
          <blockquote>
            Because your story deserves more than ordinary photographs. It deserves images with identity.
          </blockquote>
          <img
            src="https://crismaturana.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/firma-Cristobal-Maturana.png"
            alt="Cristóbal Maturana signature"
            class="signature"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Matufoto/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
              Facebook
            </a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
              Twitter
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/cristobalmaturanaphoto/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/></svg>
              Instagram
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 700px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
  }

  .about-body p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-white);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .signature {
    height: 50px;
    width: auto;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    filter: invert(1);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-links a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
